# Adding JSON Links to Markdown Reports

## Overview

| Item | Details |
| ------ | --------- |
| Date | 2026-01-08 |
| Objective | Add links to JSON result files in markdown reports for easy access to structured data |
| Outcome | Operational |

| Attribute | Value |
